transcript:
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Hello.
Customer: Haan ji.
Executive: Haan ji sir, main Uday bol raha hoon IndiaMART se.
Customer: Haan ji sir, bataiye.
Executive: Sir aapse baat hui thi na, aapne bola tha documents jo hain wo send karwa doge aap. Abhi tak aaye nahi documents.
Customer: Bheje nahi abhi?
Executive: Nahi nahi nahi aaye.
Customer: Main bhai se bolta hoon, to main unhe unhe send kiya tha na. Asal mein main bahar tha na.
Executive: Haan sir, humne message bhi kar diya tha unko.
Customer: Chalo main karwata hoon.
Executive: Theek hai theek hai theek hai sir.
Customer: Theek hai. Main unse baat karta hoon.
summary:

- Customer stated he was out of town and will ask his brother to send them.
